<C>__{gibson}
<D>__{oh, yeah. damn. my watch is busted.}
<C>__{frank}
<D>__{hey, rookie. be cool. just stay with me. this is what we do.}
<C>__{gibson}
<P>__{(still tapping his watch)}
<D>__{i seem nervous, huh?}
<A>__{frank laughs. gibson grins, relaxes a bit. frank checks his rolex diver's watch. multiple sirens fill the dawn.}
<C>__{frank}
